text: Rolf Nordgren (born 8 August 1946) is a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1972 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:People from Gävle
